title: BRINGING THE WAR TO THE EMPIRE - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #6
description:
BRINGING THE WAR TO THE EMPIRE - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #6 - After a few decisive battles, we now have time to turtle up and march vast armies to the Empire. This could be the turning point of the war or it could be disaster.  The next couple battles MUST be victories! The Rebellion must continue on!  Enjoy the Episode :D 

Mod link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/the-elder-scrolls-total-war
